A 37 year old man who held his girlfriend hostage in Soweto, Tladi has shot and killed himself ending a more than 12-hour hostage drama.His girlfriend was wounded after he had tried to kill her too. She has been taken to hospital.Police spent the day monitoring the situation in Tladi after they were alerted to the hostage situation.According to reports neighbours heard the couple arguing in the early hours of Wednesday morning. The man shot himself and his girlfriend is wounded. She has been taken to the hospital but she is in a stable condition, police spokesperson Lungelo Dlamini said. The man died at the scene. A case of attempted murder, kidnapping and possession of unlicensed firearm is being investigated. &nbsp;-Ntsako Mashaba